data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bath home with private covered patio has an awesome wooded preserve view! The perfect place for your morning coffee or evening wine-down! The kitchen features smooth top range, granite counters with under mount sink, all stainless steel appliances, quiet dishwasher, a large island bar and corner pantry. Split bedroom layout allows 3 front bedrooms or 2 bedrooms and an office with and a private master bedroom on the other side of house. You will love the impeccable wood look vinyl flooring throughout with Frieze carpet in the bedrooms. The Smart Home Connect technology package includes your video doorbell, keyless entry and more(tenant will have to sign up to use). Fabric hurricane window protection is also included. The Preserve at Deer Creek Phase 2 has a great community pool with seating, a grilling area, outdoor lighting and Cabana bath house. Plus community outdoor area for entertaining. Popular West Pensacola area easy access to interstate I10, Navy Federal Credit Union, restaurants and shopping. Owner has installed ceiling fans and blinds throughout! Move in ready! Pets considered with owner's prior approval and $325 non refundable pet fee per pet. No insurance restricted breeds permitted. No Smoker's. Roommates if owner approved must apply separately and qualify individually. *This is a new home for us. More photos to be uploaded soon!
